author: fitz
msg: Fix issue #2280 so that svn:mime-type is automatically set on
messiness by calling dav_svn_fs_check_path first instead of
unconditionally calling svn_fs_apply_textdelta.  Then, if we're
using autoversioning and we've got a content type from our request,
*and* the svn:mime-type prop doesn't already exist, set
svn:mime-type of our path based on the request's content type.
